luate%20her%20relationship%20with%20money%2C%20which%20was%20affecting%20her%20spending%20habits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe's%20now%20debt-free%20and%20runs%20a%20financial%20education%20company.%20She%20specializes%20in%20money%20trauma.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlejandra%20Rojas%20was%20raised%20by%20two%20accountants%20in%20Cali%2C%20Colombia%20and%20helped%20them%20with%20bookkeeping%20to%20earn%20an%20allowance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20play%20with%20invoices%20as%20a%20kid%20instead%20of%20dolls%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20understood%20basic%20money%20principles%20from%20a%20young%20age%20and%20continued%20her%20financial%20education%20as%20a%20university%20student.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20graduated%20as%20a%20finance%20professional%2C%20so%20I%20knew%20every%20strategy%20in%20the%20book%20on%20how%20to%20save%2C%20how%20to%20get%20out%20of%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rojas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20those%20skills%20didn't%20translate%20in%20the%20real%20world.%20After%20landing%20a%20job%20as%20a%20financial%20officer%20in%20Washington%20DC%2C%20she%20started%20spending%20more%20than%20she%20was%20earning%20and%20found%20herself%20in%20a%20%2410%2C000%20hole.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20into%20credit%20card%20debt%20from%20mindless%20spending%20%E2%80%94%20what%20you%20would%20now%20call%20'doom%20spending%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Rojas.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20a%20young%20professional%20in%20DC.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20to%20go%20to.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20happy%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccumulating%20debt%20as%20a%20finance%20professional%20was%20confusing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20have%20spent%20the%20last%20decade%20studying%20and%20growing%20up%20knowing%20about%20money%2C%20why%20am%20I%20acting%20this%20way%3F%20It%20was%20this%20misalignment%20between%20what%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20be%20doing%20and%20what%20I%20was%20actually%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rojas%2C%20who%20also%20recalls%20feeling%20shame%20and%20guilt.%20It%20held%20her%20back%20from%20talking%20to%20anyone%20about%20her%20finances.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20easy%20to%20say%2C%20'Well%2C%20I%20am%20in%20this%20amount%20of%20debt%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20to%20get%20out%20of%20it.'%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20judgment%20that%20comes%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22alejandra%20rojas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67214cba9b3250dbbceaf849%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERojas%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20The%20Money%20Mindset%20Hub.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alejandra%20Rojas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERojas%20wanted%20to%20understand%20her%20situation.%20She%20recalls%20Googling%20something%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20do%20finance%20people%20get%20into%20debt%3F%26quot%3B%20It%20sent%20her%20down%20the%20rabbit%20hole%20of%20money%20and%20psychology%20and%20eventually%20led%20her%20to%20get%20a%20Trauma%20of%20Money%20certification.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20learned%20that%20her%20%26quot%3Bdoom%20spending%26quot%3B%20habits%20were%20emotional%20and%20stemmed%20from%20a%20fear%20of%20losing%20her%20friends%20or%20not%20being%20able%20to%20connect%20with%20her%20community.%20Understanding%20why%20she%20was%20overspending%20was%20empowering.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20wasn't%20the%20only%20one%20%E2%80%94%20that%20this%20was%20not%20a%20'me%20problem'%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20it%20was%20something%20that%20I%20could%20turn%20around%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20did%20was%20make%20a%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rojas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227aa095df-e837-4e71-ad71-c8ce5eb1dfb9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHer%202-step%20process%20to%20getting%20out%20of%20debt%3A%20Creating%20a%20'big%20vision'%20and%20using%20the%20'snowball%20method'%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20years%2C%20Rojas%20didn't%20know%20what%20she%20wanted%2C%20let%20alone%20have%20a%20plan%20for%20getting%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20just%20going%20day%20by%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20first%20sit%20down%20and%20say%2C%20'Where%20do%20I%20want%20to%20be%20in%20three%20years%20from%20now%3F%20In%20five%20years%20from%20now%3F%20What%20is%20the%20thing%20that%20I%20want%20for%20myself%3F'%20And%20that%20step%20alone%20showed%20a%20complete%20misalignment%20of%20how%20I%20was%20spending%20and%20where%20I%20wanted%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20thought%20through%20what%20she%20calls%20her%20%26quot%3Bbig%20vision%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20was%20two-fold%3A%20to%20travel%20the%20world%20and%20build%20a%20business.%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20the%20second%20step%20was%2C%20'Okay%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20be%20there%20in%20five%20years%2C%20what%20do%20I%20need%20to%20do%20now%2C%20and%20how%20would%20I%20pay%20this%20debt%20off%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20used%20what's%20known%20as%20the%20debt%20snowball%20method.%20With%20this%20strategy%2C%20you%20make%20the%20minimum%20payment%20on%20each%20debt%20except%20for%20your%20smallest%20one%20%E2%80%94%20on%20that%20one%2C%20you%20pay%20as%20much%20as%20your%20budget%20allows%20you%20to%20each%20month.%20The%20idea%20is%20that%20you%20gain%20positive%20momentum%20by%20checking%20debts%20off%20the%20list.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20needed%20the%20motivation%20that%20comes%20from%2C%20'Okay%2C%20I%20did%20this.%20I%20paid%20this%20one%2C'%26quot%3B%20said%20Rojas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20free%20up%20cash%20to%20pay%20down%20her%20debt%2C%20she%20felt%20she%20had%20only%20one%20lever%20to%20pull%3A%20spend%20less.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20no%20option%20for%20me%20to%20boost%20my%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20trapped%20in%20a%20cap%2C%20so%20I%20could%20only%20control%20my%20expenses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22alejandra%20rojas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67214d7201ea6d83dee4f281%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERojas%20and%20her%20daughter%20split%20their%20time%20between%20Maryland%20and%20Amsterdam.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alejandra%20Rojas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20started%20by%20examining%20her%20credit%20card%20statements%20and%20spending%20habits.%20It%20was%20a%20revealing%20exercise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20look%20back%20to%20what%20I%20was%20spending%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20literally%20pleasing%20everybody%20but%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20absolutely%20nothing%20that%20showed%20up%20that%20could%20bring%20me%20long-term%20joy%20%E2%80%94%20none%20of%20that.%20It%20was%20just%20in-the-moment%20purchases%20and%20things%20that%20I%20don't%20even%20remember.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20started%20tracking%20her%20expenses%20so%20she%20knew%20exactly%20where%20her%20money%20was%20going.%20Some%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20like%20rent%2C%20groceries%2C%20and%20insurance%20%E2%80%94%20were%20unavoidable%2C%20but%20she%20wanted%20all%20other%20expenses%20to%20feel%20intentional.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20dollar%20that%20went%20out%2C%20I%20knew%20exactly%20the%20purpose%20that%20it%20had%2C%20and%20how%20it%20was%20going%20to%20