0are%20increasingly%20turning%20to%20AI%20chatbots%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-gpt-4o-productivity-hacks-for-work-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20help%20them%20compare%20products%20and%20decide%20on%20purchases%2C%20and%20one%20company%20just%20launched%20a%20new%20tool%20that%20shows%20brands%20how%20they%20stack%20up%20against%20the%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%2C%20Evertune%2C%20launched%20from%20stealth%20today%20with%20%244%20million%20in%20seed%20funding%2C%20it%20confirmed%20exclusively%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20New%20York%20VC%20firm%20Eniac%20Ventures%20led%20the%20funding%20round%2C%20with%20seed-stage%20firm%20NextView%20Ventures%20and%20angel%20investor%20Roger%20Ehrenberg%20also%20participating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%20April%2C%20Evertune%20is%20a%20brand%20analytics%20platform%20that%20focuses%20specifically%20on%20what%20AI%20models%20say%20about%20a%20particular%20brand%20or%20product.%20The%20startup%20tells%20companies%20the%20probability%20that%20an%20LLM%20would%20recommend%20the%20brand%20to%20consumers%2C%20compares%20companies%20to%20their%20competitors%2C%20and%20identifies%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20currently%20integrated%20with%20LLMs%2C%20including%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%2C%20Google's%20Gemini%2C%20Meta's%20Llama%2C%20Anthropic's%20Claude%2C%20and%20Perplexity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Stempeck%2C%20one%20of%20Evertune's%20co-founders%20and%20the%20startup's%20CEO%2C%20said%20he%20was%20inspired%20to%20start%20building%20the%20company%20about%20a%20year%20ago%20when%20he%20was%20deciding%20which%20car%20he%20should%20purchase%20for%20his%20family.%20He%20ended%20up%20querying%20ChatGPT%20to%20summarize%20different%20vehicle%20specifications%20rather%20than%20searching%20Google%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20realized%20that%20other%20consumers%20were%20also%20starting%20to%20turn%20to%20LLMs%20for%20shopping%20help%2C%20Stempeck%20%E2%80%94%20an%20early%20employee%20at%20then-startup%20The%20Trade%20Desk%2C%20a%20programmatic%20marketing%20company%20that%20offers%20personalized%20digital%20advertising%20that%20IPO'd%20in%202016%20%E2%80%94%20realized%20that%20there%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20help%20brands%20get%20ahead%20of%20the%20competition%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20changes%20we've%20seen%20in%20the%20search%20space%2C%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BLLMs%20get%20straight%20to%20the%20answer%20instead%20of%20having%20to%20click%20and%20do%20your%20own%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20marketing%20team%20standpoint%2C%20knowing%20what%20these%20LLMs%20are%20saying%20about%20a%20brand%2C%20product%2C%20or%20competitor%20becomes%20really%20important%20at%20scale%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20adopting%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrands%20can%20also%20use%20Evertune%20to%20improve%20what%20LLMs%20say%20about%20them%2C%20similar%20to%20how%20they%20optimize%20SEO%20to%20appear%20at%20the%20top%20of%20a%20Google%20search.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20luxury%20retail%20brand%20recently%20trained%20a%20model%20using%20the%20company's%20existing%20employee%20handbooks%2C%20Stempeck%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-adtech-startups-2023-11%23adventr-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGenerative%20AI%20startups%20in%20the%20marketing%20and%20adtech%20space%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20booming%20%E2%80%94%20although%2C%20unlike%20Evertune's%20focus%20on%20LLM%20analytics%2C%20many%20other%20startups%20in%20the%20space%20focus%20on%20generating%20marketing%20materials%20like%20copy%2C%20photos%20and%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20analytics%20side%2C%20Chalice%20builds%20algorithms%20for%20advertisers%20to%20use%20in%20the%20software%20where%20they%20purchase%20digital%20ads%