%26quot%3Ban%20inconclusive%20report%26quot%3B%20-%20over%20eight%20months%20-%20was%20also%20flagged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Anupinder%20Singh%20and%20Lapita%20Banerji%20pointed%20out%20five%20of%20the%20seven%20suspended%20officers%20were%20of%20a%20junior%20rank%20-%20only%20two%20officers%20of%20Deputy%20Superintendent-rank%2C%20Gursheer%20Singh%20and%20Sammer%20Vaneet%20were%20penalised%2C%C2%A0and%20noted%20the%20cops%20%26quot%3Ballowed%20the%20criminal%20to%20use%20electronic%20device(s)%20and%20provided%20a%20studio-like%20facility%20for%20the%20interview%2C%20which%20tends%20to%20glorify%20crime...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvolvement%20of%20senior%20cops%20suggests%20%26quot%3Billegal%20gratification%20from%20the%20criminal...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20also%20irked%20by%20copies%20of%20the%20interview%20resurfacing%20online%20despite%20a%20December%20order%20that%20it%20be%20removed%20from%20all%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20interviews%20are%20stated%20to%20have%20garnered%20over%2012%20million%20views.%20It%20would%20have%20an%20adverse%20impact%20upon%20youngsters%20with%20impressionable%20minds.%20Punjab%20is%20a%20border%20state%20and%20any%20deterioration%20in%20law%20and%20order%20or%20increase%20in%20crime%20could%20affect%20national%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECopies%20of%20the%20interview%20resurfaced%20online%20after%20the%20October%2013%20murder%20of%20Maharashtra%20politician%20Baba%20Siddiqui%2C%20who%20was%20a%20member%20of%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20faction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20in%20the%20interview%20Bishnoi%20-%20%26quot%3Binvolved%20in%2071%20cases%20in%20the%20State%20of%20Punjab%20and%20convicted%20in%20four%20cases%2C%20which%20includes%20offences%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20(which%20is%20the%20anti-t