%20despite%20not%20receiving%20any%20response%20from%20her.%20He%20called%20her%20at%20least%20five%20times%20in%20a%20row%20and%20even%20requested%20to%20hear%20her%20voice%20for%20a%20second%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20just%20asking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20screenshot%20shows%20a%20man%20sending%20love%20poetry%20to%20Harshita%20after%20being%20rejected%20for%20a%20job.%20When%20asked%20for%20feedback%2C%20Harshita%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNeed%20improvement.%20Not%20fit%20for%20us.%E2%80%9D%20Soon%20after%20the%20rejected%20candidate%20started%20sending%20her%20love%20poems%20hinting%20that%20he%20could%20not%20live%20without%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20end%20there.%20Another%20candidate%20first%20asked%20for%20a%20second%20chance%20to%20share%20a%20revised%20resume%20or%20%E2%80%9Cproper%20CV%E2%80%9D.%20He%20even%20asked%20for%20the%20years%20of%20experience%20required%20for%20the%20role.%20But%20within%20minutes%2C%20he%20changed%20the%20course%20of%20the%20conversation%20and%20went%20on%20to%20pass%20lewd%20remarks%20on%20her%20physical%20appearance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20were%20looking%20hawwt%20that%20day!%E2%80%9D%20he%20texted%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20had%20not%20been%20able%20to%20%26quot%3Bsleep%20or%20wake%20up%26quot%3B%20since%20he%20saw%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarshita%20shared%20screenshots%20without%20hiding%20mobile%20numbers%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexpose%E2%80%9D%20the%20offenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI'm%20committed%20to%20maintaining%20a%20respectful%20and%20calm%20demeanor%2C%20even%20in%20the%20face%20of%20inappropriate%20behavior.%20Don't%20mistake%20this%20for%20my%20weakness%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20people%20who%20cannot%20maintain%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20a%20basic%20level%20of%20professionalism%20have%20already%20failed%20-%20both%20as%20a%20professional%20and%20as%20a%20human%20being%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetizens%20are%20in%20shock.%20Many%20users%20went%20on%20to%20advise%20Harshita%20on%20what%20she%20should%20do%20or%20should%20have%20done%20in%20such%20a%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20saying%20its%20your%20fault%E2%80%A6%20but%20you%20will%20have%20to%20contact%20with%20the%20employees%20through%20official%20email%20instead%20of%20whatsapp%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20commented%20one%20LinkedIn%20user.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSadly%2C%20any%20woman%2C%20by%20default%2C%20is%20not%20safe%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20another%20and%20shared%20five%20tips%20including%20not%20sharing%20one's%20personal%20number%2C%20asking%20the%20organisation%20to%20divide%20the%20list%20of%20candidates%20gender-wise%2C%20and%20quitting%20if%20the%20company%20isn't%20doing%20anything%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDon't%20wait%20for%20ten%20messages%2C%20you%20can%20simply%20block%20unknown%20people%20who%20text%20you%20at%20midnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730275740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fc3u2rgl_hr-receives-creepy-messages_625x300_30_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcute-hawwt-hr-highlights-creepy-messages-from-rejected-candidates-6906635%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20HR%20professional%20from%20Noida%20has%20shared%20screenshots%20of%20inappropriate%20messages%20she%20received%20from%20candidates%20who%20weren't%20selected%20for%20a%20job.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20'Flying%20BMW'%20Video%20Goes%20Viral%2C%20Gurugram's%20Quick%20Action%20On%20Speed%20Breaker%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20a%20video%20showed%20cars%20%26quot%3Bflying%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20a%20speed%20breaker%20on%20Gurugram's%20Golf%20Course%20road%2C%20authorities%20swung%20into%20action%20and%20installed%20a%20cautionary%20signboard.%3C%2F