3Cp%3EThe%20party's%20allies%2C%20most%20notably%20the%20Thackeray%20Sena%2C%20were%20angered%20by%20what%20they%20said%20was%20the%20Congress'%20failure%20to%20accommodate%20smaller%20and%20regional%20partners.%20The%20Thackeray%20Sena's%20jabs%20-%20published%20in%20party%20mouthpiece%20Saamana%20-%20drew%20an%20immediate%20response%20from%20the%20Congress'%20Maharashtra%20office%2C%20which%20said%20it%20valued%20their%20allies%20and%20would%20not%20act%20as%20the%20Haryana%20unit%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-haryana-assembly-election-results-shiv-sena-editorial-saamana-arrogant-overconfident-congress-allies-on-warpath-after-haryana-loss-6749949%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BArrogant%2C%20Overconfident%26quot%3B%3A%20Allies%20Twist%20Knife%20In%20Congress%20Over%20Haryana%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20differences%20within%20the%20Mahayuti...%20the%20BJP's%20stealing%20of%20seats%20from%20allies%20is%20a%20clear%20message%20it%20wants%20to%20kill%20off%20its%20allies.%20But%20we%20(the%20MVA)%20are%20together...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chennithala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20no%20'friendly%20fight'%20within%20the%20MVA%2C%20he%20stressed%2C%20referring%20to%20unfortunate%20situations%20in%20the%20April-June%20general%20election%20that%20saw%20occasions%20in%20which%20members%20of%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20fielded%20candidates%20for%20the%20same%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20MVA%20is%20concerned%2C%20as%20of%20Tuesday%20evening%20it%20appeared%20the%20Congress%20had%20nominated%20103%20candidates%2C%20while%20the%20Thackeray%20Sena%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%20had%20named%2087%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20each%20case%20it%20was%20over%20the%2085%20per%20party%20agreed%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%2011%20remaining%20seats%20are%20expected