Tuesday.%20Bilal%20Ansari%2C%2022%2C%20and%20Shuheb%20Qureshi%2C%2021%2C%20both%20natives%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Bulandshahr%2C%20were%20arrested%20during%20a%20shootout%2C%20three%20days%20after%20they%20carried%20out%20the%20shooting%20in%20North%20West%20Delhi's%20Rani%20Bagh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20accused%2C%20who%20were%20on%20a%20bike%2C%20fired%20multiple%20rounds%20to%20extort%20Rs%2015%20crore%20from%20the%20Delhi%20businessman%20and%20left%20a%20slip%20bearing%20the%20name%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BKaushal%20Chaudhary%20-%20Pawan%20Shokeen%20-%20Bambhia%20Gang.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20they%20told%20the%20police%20that%20gangster%20Pawan%20Shaukeen%2C%20who%20has%20fled%20from%20India%20and%20is%20currently%20operating%20from%20the%20US%2C%20had%20ordered%20them%20to%20open%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Pawan%20Shaukeen%20Hired%20The%20Shooters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawan%20Shaukeen%2C%20who%20was%20an%20arms%20supplier%20in%20Delhi%2C%20met%20one%20of%20the%20shooters%2C%20Bilal%2C%20when%20he%20was%20working%20in%20a%20factory%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesg's%20Khurja%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20contacted%20him%20and%20asked%20to%20do%20a%20recce%20of%20the%20residence%20of%20the%20businessman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPawan%20also%20told%20him%20he%20would%20be%20paid%20for%20the%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilal%20then%20contacted%20Shuheb%2C%20whom%20he%20had%20met%20through%20a%20common%20friend%20who%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20Pawan%20Shokeen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gangster%20told%20both%20to%20fire%20upon%20the%20residence%20in%20the%20Rani%20Bagh%20area.%20While%20Shuheb%20was%20driving%20the%20bike%2C%20Bilal%20carried%20out%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERise%20Of%20Extortion%20Bids%20In%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20has%20witnessed%20a%20spate%20of%20firing%20incidents%20as%20part%20of%20extortion%20attempts