f%20a%20%26quot%3Bsweets%20person.%26quot%3B%20Sure%2C%20I'll%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fina-garten-best-dessert-recipes-review-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elook%20at%20the%20dessert%20menu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20more%20out%20of%20curiosity%20than%20from%20a%20desire%20to%20eat%20something%20sweet%20at%20the%20end%20of%20my%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202021%2C%20I've%20probably%20eaten%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-add-to-chocolate-chip-cookies-to-make-better-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echocolate-chip%20cookies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ice%20cream%20cones%2C%20Italian%20ice%20cups%2C%20and%20candy%20bars%20than%20I%20did%20during%20my%20entire%20childhood.%20Initially%2C%20I%20chalked%20it%20up%20to%20bad%20habits%20I%20picked%20up%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20came%20the%20acne%2C%20fatigue%2C%20brain%20fog%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fnight-sweats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enight%20sweats%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20sleeplessness%2C%20and%20midsection%20weight%20gain.%20I%20knew%20something%20was%20going%20on%20in%20my%20body%2C%20but%20I%20had%20no%20language%20for%20it.%20It%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20going%20through%20puberty%20all%20over%20again%20%E2%80%94%20but%20how%20could%20that%20be%20in%20my%20late%2030s%3F%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20did%20I%20know%20second%20puberty%20is%20not%20an%20official%20term%20but%20one%20used%20regularly%20when%20talking%20about%20perimenopause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223c227a24-f7e2-4c68-ab34-93f94509c59c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20one%20in%20my%20life%20was%20talking%20about%20perimenopause%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20I%20told%20some%20friends%20around%20my%20age%20about%20my%20sugar%20cravings%2C%20and%20both%20women%20confirmed%20that%20they%2C%20too%2C%20had%20been%20eating%20excess%20sweets%2C%20having%20brain%20fog%2C%20experiencing%20mood%20swings%2C%20and%20gaining%20belly%20fat.%20I%20realized%20that%20my%20situation%20wasn't%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20them%2C%20a%20registered%20nurse%2C%20referenced%20a%20term%20I%20had%20heard%20in%20passing%20but%20didn't%20really%20understand%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperimenopause-pregnant-late-period-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperimenopause%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20explained%20that%20it%20was%20basically%20like%20%26quot%3Bbaby%20menopause%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20similar%20but%20sometimes%20fewer%20or%20milder%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20explanation%20helped%20me%20understand%20why%20I%20always%20seemed%20to%20sweat%20excessively%20when%20no%20one%20else%20was.%20I%20went%20to%20the%20gym%20several%20days%20a%20week%2C%20taking%20barre%2C%20pilates%2C%20kickboxing%2C%20boxing%2C%20dance%2C%20and%20sometimes%20cycling%2C%20and%20while%20my%20arms%20and%20legs%20were%20sculpted%20and%20strong%2C%20my%20lower%20belly%20continued%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'd%20think%20with%20five%20older%20sisters%2C%20I'd%20have%20had%20some%20inkling%20that%20when%20I%20entered%20my%20late%2030s%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthese-doctors-have-seen-many-pregnancies-after-40-during-perimenopause-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%2040s%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20may%20come%20to%20expect%20this.%20But%20at%20age%2039%2C%20when%20the%20symptoms%20seemed%20to%20reach%20a%20peak%2C%20I%20felt%20so%20unprepared%2C%20even%20betrayed%20to%20some%20degree.%20Why%20isn't%20anyone%20around%20me%20talking%20about%20perimenopause%3F%20I%20heard%20about%20menopause%20but%20thought%20it%20was%20something%20that%20happened%20in%20your%2050s.%20As%20an%20elder%20millennial%2C%20I%20feel%20we%20are%20unearthing%20things%20because%20previous%20generations%20thought%20they%20were%20too%20taboo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224235b989-a15a-4ade-ae70-91204e289079%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20perimenopause%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20contacted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrbrandyemd.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrandye%20Manigat%2C%20a%20board-certified%20OB%2FGYN%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20specializes%20in%20midlife%2C%20perimenopause%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-shares-frustrations-of-going-through-menopause-at-age-49-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenopause%20transitions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20get%20some%20answers%20to%20my%20questions.%20She%20said%20there%20are%20several%20reasons%20women%20may%20shy%20away%20from%20talking%20about%20perimenopause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManigat%20said%20that%20perimenopause%20is%20the%20transitional%20period%20before%20entering%20menopause.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20typically%20somewhere%20around%20early%20to%20late%2040s%20when%20women%20start%20to%20experience%20the%20symptoms%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20constellation%20of%20things%20versus%20one%20single%20thing%20that%20you%20may%20notice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20symptoms%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20mine%20included%20subtle%20hot%20flashes%2C%20unusual%20waves%20of%20emotion%2C%20knee%20and%20back%20pain%2C%20painful%20cramps%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fsigns-youre-losing-too-much-blood-during-period%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheavy%20bleeding%20during%20my%20periods%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20way%20to%20know%20if%20you're%20experiencing%20perimenopause%20is%20by%20talking%20to%20your%20doctor.%20When%20my%20symptoms%20first%20hit%2C%20I%20saw%20several%20different%20kinds%20of%20specialists%20to%20get%20answers%2C%20but%20perimenopause%20never%20crossed%20my%20mind%20until%20it%20was%20suggested%20by%20my%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252b1586e-9b85-44f1-ac83-492c1696150b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20what%20I'm%20doing%20to%20deal%20with%20my%20perimenopause%20symptoms%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EManigat%20said%20hot%20flashes%2C%20a%20common%20perimenopause%20symptom%2C%20can%20exacerbate%20dehydration.%20She%20recommends%20hydrating%20with%20electrolyte%20drink%20mixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOptimizing%20your%20sleep%20can%20also%20be%20helpful.%20%26quot%3BInadequate%20sleep%20puts%20you%20in%20a%20state%20of%20fight-or-flight%2C%20which%20increases%20your%20cortisol%2C%20which%20not%20only%20deposits%20more%20fat%20into%20the%20abdominal%20area%2C%20but%20it%20also%20makes%20you%20crave%20sweets%20and%20carbs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20won't%20be%20slowing%20down%20on%20those%20fitness%20classes%20anytime%20soon%2C%20but%20I%20%3Cem%3Ewill%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20making%20some%20lifestyle%20changes%20at%20Manigat's%20recommendation%2C%20like%20powering%20down%20my%20electronics%20earlier%2C%20reading%20before%20bed%20instead%20of%20watching%20TV%2C%20and%20taking%20long%20baths%20in%20the%20evening%20to%20relax%20to%20help%20with%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20deal%20with%20something%20when%20you%20have%20people%20around%20you%20who%20can%20offer%20advice%20and%20ideas%20based%20on%20their%20experiences.%20So%2C%20my%20friends%20and%20I%20plan%20to%20talk%20about%20this%20at%20brunch%2C%20at%20the%20boxing%20workout%2C%20at%20the%20pool%2C%20at%20the%20nail%20salon%2C%20and%20at%20dinner%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%2C%20I%20feel%20a%20little%20silly%20about%20all%20of%20it.%20But%20I%20know%20that%20talking%20about%20perimenopause%20can%20be%20helpful%20to%20other%20women%20who%20are%20feeling%20the%20same%20way.%20Going%20forward%2C%20I'll%20allow%20my%20feelings%20and%20show%20grace%20to%20myself%20and%20other%20women%20entering%20second%20puberty%20with%20no%20clue%20what%20they're%20in%20store%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%2