ADHD)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecan%20leave%20individuals%20feeling%20isolated.%20For%20Aalen%20Issac%2C%20a%20senior%20content%20associate%20at%20Alyve%20Health%2C%20this%20battle%20has%20shaped%20his%20professional%20life%20and%20made%20him%20resilient%20in%20achieving%20his%20goals.%20Aalen%E2%80%99s%20journey%20with%20ADHD%20began%20long%20before%20his%20diagnosis%20at%20age%2024.%20He%20first%20encountered%20the%20term%20when%20his%20youngest%20brother%20was%20diagnosed%20as%20a%20child%2C%20prompting%20their%20family%20to%20consider%20testing%20for%20all%20the%20siblings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20Aalen%20had%20struggled%20with%20attention%20issues%20growing%20up%2C%20he%20had%20never%20received%20a%20diagnosis%20before%20that.%20In%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20he%20discusses%20his%20experience%20with%20ADHD%2C%20sharing%20the%20challenges%20he%20faces%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F264065%2Fwhat-is-invisible-disability-workplace-autism-depression-adhd-policy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoping%20strategies%20he%20employs%20at%20work%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20offers%20valuable%20insights%20for%20others%20with%20ADHD%20navigating%20the%20workspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20experiencing%20difficulties%20with%20attention%20throughout%20his%20life%2C%20Aalen%20sought%20help%20for%20anxiety%20three%20years%20ago%20and%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20something%20known%20as%20executive%20dysfunction%2C%20and%20I%20learnt%20about%20it%20very%20late%20in%20life.%20It%E2%80%99s%20like%20a%20mental%20block%20essentially.%20