rg.in%2Fwildlife-biodiversity%2Findia-has-718-snow-leopards-most-of-them-live-in-unprotected-areas-centre-94174%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoint%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%20other%20non-profit%20organisations%20on%2030%20January%202024%2C%20there%20are%20just%20718%20snow%20leopards%20in%20India%2C%20of%20which%20only%20a%20third%20are%20under%20legal%20protection.%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EStatus%20Report%20of%20Snow%20Leopards%20in%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%20that%20barely%2034%25%20of%20the%201%2C20%2C000%20square%20kilometres%20of%20snow%20leopard%20habitat%20in%20India%20is%20legally%20protected.%20Less%20than%2070%25%20of%20this%20predator%E2%80%99s%20habitat%20remains%20unprotected.%20%3Cem%3E(Above%20images%20of%20Dr%20Tsewang%20Namgail%2C%20a%20snow%20leopard%20%26amp%3B%20Charudutt%20Mishra)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20figures%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20for%20local%20communities%20to%20be%20engaged%20in%20the%20conservation%20of%20this%20threatened%20species.%20Here%20are%20eight%20conservationists%20who%20have%20done%20incredible%20work%20in%20not%20only%20understanding%20snow%20leopards%20but%20also%20engaging%20local%20communities%20to%20protect%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECharudutt%20Mishra%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECharudutt%20Mishra%20(Charu)%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Snow%20Leopard%20Trust%2C%20is%20considered%20by%20many%20as%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20foremost%20expert%20on%20snow%20leopard%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20pioneer%20of%20the%20community-based%20conservation%20model%20and%20has%20spent%20nearly%2